<p class="ql-align-justify"> <strong>第四项 擒敌术</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201022/227c3cbff2b74e2aa9ad7beab8a6c6f5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
